library(readxl)

test<- read_excel("E:/COSAS DE OSCAR DEFINITIVO/OSCAR/2020-2/Proyecto- PAPA/ANOMALIAS/ANOMALIAS POR CLUSTER/entrada pror departamento/boyaca/C3/tmed_boy_C3.xlsx",

test_PCP<- read_excel("E:/COSAS DE OSCAR DEFINITIVO/OSCAR/2020-2/Proyecto- PAPA/ANOMALIAS/ANOMALIAS POR CLUSTER/entrada pror departamento/boyaca/C3/PCP_boy_C3.xlsx", 
    sheet = "Hoja2")
test_PCP
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
library(zoo)
library(ggfortify)
library(forecast)

tmed.ts=ts(test$prom,start = 1981,frequency = 12)
arima_tmed<-auto.arima(tmed.ts)
forecast_tmed<-forecast(arima_tmed,level = c(95), h = 60)
PCP.ts=ts(test_PCP$prom,start = 1981,frequency = 12)
arima_PCP<-auto.arima(PCP.ts)
forecast_PCP<-forecast(arima_PCP,level = c(95), h = 60)

pred_tmed_C4=autoplot(forecast_tmed)+xlab("Ao")+ylab("Temperatura media [C]")+ggtitle("Pronostico Temperatura media C4 - Boyac",subtitle = "Periodo 1981-2025")

pred_PCP_C4=autoplot(forecast_PCP)+xlab("Ao")+ylab("Precipitacion [mm]")+ggtitle("Precipitacion C4 - Boyac",subtitle = "Periodo 1981-2025")

pred_tmed_C4

pred_PCP_C4


ao=c(2021:2025)
meses=c("ao","enero","febrero","marzo","abril","mayo","junio","julio","agosto","septiembre","octubre","noviembre","diciembre")
tmed_fut=matrix(forecast_tmed$mean)
tmed_fut=matrix(tmed_fut,12,5)
tmed_fut=data.frame(ao,t(tmed_fut))
names(tmed_fut)=meses
tmed_fut
PCP_fut=matrix(forecast_PCP$mean)
PCP_fut=matrix(PCP_fut,12,5)
PCP_fut=data.frame(ao,t(PCP_fut))
names(PCP_fut)=meses
PCP_fut

write.csv(tmed_fut,"tmed_fut_C4_boy.csv")
write.csv(PCP_fut,"PCP_fut_C4_boy.csv")
